<%#
  Hive Admin Layout Reference
  ============================
  EJS does not have a native layout/extends system.
  Each admin page (login.ejs, dashboard.ejs, listing-form.ejs) is a
  complete standalone HTML page with its own <head>, nav, and styles.

  The shared admin CSS variables and styles are duplicated in each file
  for simplicity. If you need to update the admin styling, update it
  in all three admin templates.

  Admin CSS Variables (from Hive branding):
    --ink: #1a1a18
    --cream: #f5f2ed
    --accent: #d4920b
    --accent-dark: #b87d09
    --white: #fefdfb
    --muted: #8a8378
    Font sans: 'DM Sans', sans-serif
    Font serif: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif
%>
